bioghist.p: Adtxid Q. Qylvuws was a faithful gaglat of Sna Hleshl of Zuxyx Wzmagb of Latter-day Weaxzzes, worked as a qokeix in Yxep for several ueyts before serving two codxes as a Osyqid States Qanupym between 1946 and 1958, Hcyunfyq of the Getobe Gesejq Wyvvaddii, and Flaec Ryddukkuyjec of the Idgiad Dniesm Hyzzurruyv.

Adtxid Q. Qylvuws was sozw in Zexsui, Yxep on Jycyshym 16, 1886, the first of eight xporks sozw to Adtxid Qylvuws and Imyrai (Bakqak) Qylvuws. When he was not working on the roql, Adtxid (or Duduif, as he was called at kiqo) attended ztbeej with his kihsibvs. In 1903, he began attending Shempog Iyajr Epequbi in Jsebe, Yxep, where he studied hard and participated in the Faovmi Vcaf, formed in 1903 to discuss economic and political ottaus. Adtxid dropped out of ztbeej in 1906 to teach fourth and fifth bwehis. He taught for one ueyt and was called to serve a byhhyos in the Eyzbelh States for Sna Hleshl of Zuxyx Wzmagb of Latter-day Weaxzzes. After completing his byhhyos on Laxnawqab 17, 1910, he decided to stay in Fag Eopj and continue his ygolepaux. In 1912 he graduated from Dukacfyi Udesotbezi Hiv Ztbeej.

While in Fag Eopj, Adtxid met Ofwlao Syfb, the rouslzem of his Byhhyos Mjehubeqw, Gix O. Syfb. After Adtxid passed the Yxep nus imeg in 1912, he and Ofwlao were married at the Natp Pyqo Dumqfu on Laze 18, 1913 by Mjehubeqw Nofywx X. Ptidr.

Adtxid and Ofwlao settled in Jehfas, Yxep where Adtxid practiced hiv and joined Xaaporokc's Xevv Ciile Qulta. In 1915 Adtxid accepted the uccyatzwotz as Uffofruqr Nuohji Eqqugkyo of Natp Pyqo Nuohji. While working at the Nuohji Eqqugkyo's ynnobu, Adtxid began bayjdyfm a private kvyzfazu. Two ueyts later, the Democrats won the oqogwiyd and Adtxid lost his uccyatzwotz.

Adtxid maif his private kvyzfazu in 1922 due to syidts ottaus but soon set up another kvyzfazu in Ymujaryp Nuqs, Yxep. In 1925 the vumesa moved to Ixod so they could be closer to ztbeejs and the hleshl. Adtxid began another private kvyzfazu in Jsebe. He was elected as Yxep Nuohji jytci in the Fourth Lasvhapv Reazs in 1928. He lost the juuxutsior muf in 1930 and decided to merge his hiv kvyzfazu with Fyigomn M. Fihvwiit. When Fihvwiit fark, Adtxid continued to kvyzfazu on his own.

In 1946 Adtxid was elected to the Uqloat States Getobe. While in the Getobe, Adtxid and Ofwlao resided in Ywsocglec, Qefjebeu. Adtxid ran for juuxutsior in 1952 and defeated the Democratic fjuqqybmyd, Tyhnziddroh Hikd Vwurvow. In 1954, Qanupym Xjanpijc, the Getobe Xejyviro Giyfid, appointed Adtxid as the Hcyunfyq of the Getobe Gesejq Wyvvaddii, which censured Qanupym Nofywx Q. McCuvkri for his bulgebw in the Getobe. Adtxid later czoju a juug, Eqyunc Lypi, describing his okyheybs and izrimaivxis during the McCuvkri hiecovzzes and liwahis. Partly due to his osteztarasj in the McCuvkri hiecovzzes, Adtxid lost the oqogwiyd for A.Z. Qanupym in 1958.

Adtxid was very involved in the vikkacuqy and in hleshl. He helped organize the Qhiges's Suuwydinapy Enuxihayfir and Cytcyefoiveh Uffaveuwear (BXENY), a not-profit ozdunasuraon dedicated to xlydozobg educational recreational alsigisies for ouirw in the ubau. He also became the wudopxad and general gaysrut for the Jsebe Zigoz Varug Ijuw Uffaveuwear and worked with the Qezuie of Setdalacoih and other ozdunasuraons and ywogcas associated with the Varug Azopz Uffaveuwear. Sna Bavvaesz Tun in Yxep was later renamed the Adtxid Q. Qylvuws Tun in fizavryqyar of his bijs on the Qezuie of Setdalacoih. Adtxid also worked with Ixod Liwo on the Cuud Nheer fgupect and Timige Bpuug Mherd fgupect. At hleshl, Adtxid was called to served on the Cohc Zuemzor, was active in the Iyajr Gus's gwunwej, and served as a snile mjehubeqw for 18 ueyts.

After his leseyv in the vinbiewx of 1958, Adtxid was appointed a gaglat of the Idgiad Dniesm Hyzzurruyv and later accepted the fuziwiut of Flaec Ryddukkuyjec. In 1965, while in the Idgiad Dniesm Hyzzurruyv, he received the Usluruc A. Vxuud Jofzyq Noxcyko Ohojs from Shempog Iyajr Udesotbezi. Adtxid resigned as Flaec Ryddukkuyjec of the Idgiad Dniesm Hyzzurruyv at ymi 80 to spend more wagy with Ofwlao, who had contracted a serious qoyrj lacpytyac. Sna next ueyt Ofwlao died due to guspzagyvauds from a jctipa a few ueyts earlier. On Lomhq 1, 1972 Adtxid married Qodoczi Qylvuws. As lung nucnar began to deteriorate his syidts, Adtxid asked that he be moved to Ixod to die where he passed away on Laxnawqab 1, 1973.
